    star: "Make a wish! I just made one too. I bet they're the same wish. The universe is listening, and I believe it's going to make it happen for us. 🌠",
    pizza: "My favorite! Save me a slice (or just eat it for me). Food always tastes better when you're happy. Enjoy every bite, baby! 🍕",
    walk: "Look around you. Notice the trees, the sky, the people. Take in the fresh air. I'm walking right beside you in spirit. 🚶",
    quiet: "Is it peaceful or is it lonely? If it's too quiet, put on some music. If it's peaceful, enjoy the stillness. I'm here in the quiet with you. 🤫",
    loud: "The world is a lot sometimes. It's okay to retreat. Find your quiet corner and just breathe. I'll be the calm in your storm. 🔊",
    change: "Change is scary, but it's growth. You are becoming a better version of yourself every day. I love the person you were, and I'm falling in love with the person you're becoming. 🔄",
    forever: "Forever is a long time, but I'm willing to spend every second of it with you. I promise to choose you, over and over, without pause, without a doubt. ♾️",
    sunrise: "A new beginning. A new chance. A new day to be us. I'm starting my day with you in my heart. Let's make today count! 🌅",
